        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p>
                    <bibl><ptr target="#gasperini1995"/>, p. 11, n. <citedRange>9</citedRange> (dr.) 
                        (= <bibl><ptr target="#gasperini2008"/>, pp. <citedRange>331-332</citedRange></bibl>)</bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>44.1541, 9</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#maffre2007"/> p. 173, n. <citedRange>34</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>005100</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                
                <div type="textpart" subtype="fragment" n="a">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><persName type="divine" ref="#Apollo"><name nymRef="#Ἀπόλλων"><supplied reason="lost">Ἀπό</supplied><unclear>λ</unclear>λōνι</name></persName><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                   </ab>
                </div> 
             
                <div type="textpart" subtype="fragment" n="b">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ενο</orig><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                   </ab>
                </div> 
                </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>a.<supplied reason="subaudible">Untel a dédié</supplied> à Apollon; </p>
            <p>b. intraduisible</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>a. <supplied reason="subaudible">So-and-so dedicated</supplied> to Apollo; </p>
            <p>b. not usefully translatable</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>a.<supplied reason="subaudible">Il tale ha dedicato</supplied> ad Apollo; </p>
            <p>b. intraducibile</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>غير قابل للترجمه بشكل جيد</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>Fragment b) might pertain to same inscription as a) and thus be part of the dedicant's name, but this is very uncertain.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
